{
  "texts": [
    "How the notified bodies interpret and enforce the law in practice will likely be decisive for the further development of LLMs in the biomedical sector.",
    "Our study has limitations.",
    "First, our review focused on LLM applications and limitations in patient care, thus excluding research directed at clinicians only.",
    "Future studies may extend our synthesis approach to LLM applications that explicitly focus on healthcare professionals.",
    "Second, there is a risk that potentially eligible studies were not included in our analysis if they were not present in the 5 databases reviewed or were not available in English."
  ]
}